data.eml:eml: Thysanoptera intercepted in the Netherlands on plant products from Ethiopia, with description of two new species of the genus Thrips

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Vierbergen, Gijsbertus (2014): Thysanoptera intercepted in the Netherlands on plant products from Ethiopia, with description of two new species of the genus Thrips. Zootaxa 3765 (3): 269-278, DOI: http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.3765.3.3
